It bids 8, pulls aragorn (9) and then lets frodo die and sam take the ring. Its all about sam and his def +1 ability... ;)</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Starting: (appearing in order of importance)<br />
